OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FCustomers whose storage units have
OL,7,Fbeen broken into at a site in Swansea
OL,8,Fsay they have been left thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds out of pocket and "made to feel
OL,10,Fworthless" by the experience.
OL,12,FAt least 19 units at Pink Storage on
OL,13,FLangdon Road on the outskirts of the
OL,14,Fcity were broken into around the last
OL,15,Fweekend of January 2026.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
