OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FCCTV cameras were not in place on the
OL,7,Fsite at the time of the burglary -
OL,8,Fwith ITV News understanding they had
OL,9,Fnot been in place for several months.
OL,10,FThis is despite the storage company
OL,11,Fadvertising 24/7 CCTV surveillance,
OL,12,Fperimeter fencing and security-
OL,13,Fcontrolled gates.
OL,15,FBethan and Richard Thomas, who owned
OL,16,Fone of the affected units, needed
OL,17,Fsomewhere to keep their belongings
OL,18,Fsafe while they moved house but have
OL,19,Fnow lost thousands of pounds worth of
OL,20,Fgoods and had many items damaged.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,F"Certain things have hit me hardest,"
OL,7,Fsaid Bethan. "The photographs and the
OL,8,Fmemories and the things that you can't
OL,9,Fget back."
OL,11,FThey say that they only found out
OL,12,Fabout the break-in after being made
OL,13,Faware of a social media post showing
OL,14,Ftheir belongings dumped outside.
OL,15,FBelongings that included baby photos
OL,16,Fof Bethan's now grown-up children.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FIn the aftermath of the break-in,
OL,7,FBethan filmed the damage at the
OL,8,Fstorage site. Her footage showed
OL,9,Fdamaged fencing, allowing access to
OL,10,Fthe units from outside the site. It is
OL,11,Fnot clear whether this damage already
OL,12,Fexisted or was caused by the thieves.
OL,14,FBethan said the way they have been
OL,15,Ftreated by Pink Storage has made the
OL,16,Fordeal even worse.
OL,18,FShe said: "The fact that, like, the
OL,19,Fphotos and those things were just left
OL,20,Foutside for - we don't know how long
OL,21,Fbecause they just didn't let us know."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FHer partner, Richard, said: "We've
OL,7,Fbeen made to feel like we're
OL,8,Fworthless."
OL,10,FThe couple are now desperately trying
OL,11,Fto salvage some of the possessions
OL,12,Fthey thought were going to be kept
OL,13,Fsafe.
OL,15,FAnother of the units affected was
OL,16,Frented by mum-of-two Kayleigh Baker.
OL,17,FThe experience has left her feeling
OL,18,Fanxious after thieves took documents
OL,19,Fwith names and addresses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,F"I can't sleep...It's horrible. Why
OL,7,Ftake stuff with addresses on? Why even
OL,8,Fgo through that box? It wouldn't be
OL,9,Fworth anything to anyone."
OL,11,FAmongst the belongings taken were
OL,12,Fbirthday presents she had recently
OL,13,Fbought for her son, who has complex
OL,14,Fmedical needs. In total, she thinks
OL,15,Fshe has lost around #4,000 worth of
OL,16,Fitems.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FOn their webpage, Pink Storage say
OL,7,Fthey were established more than a
OL,8,Fdecade ago and have grown into one of
OL,9,Fthe UK's leading names in self-
OL,10,Fstorage. They also say they are proud
OL,11,Fmembers of the Self Storage
OL,12,FAssociation and are compliant with
OL,13,Ftheir high-standards and rules.
OL,15,FSelf Storage Association Limited (SSA
OL,16,FUK) said that until recently, Pink
OL,17,FStorage was on its Subscriber Scheme -
OL,18,Fa scheme designed to support operators
OL,19,Fthat do not meet their standards and
OL,20,Fthat the Subscriber Scheme is not SSA
OL,21,FUK membership.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FShe said she is angry that the
OL,7,Fsecurity measures she believed she was
OL,8,Fpaying for, like CCTV, were not in
OL,9,Fplace. Pink Storage said South Wales
OL,10,FPolice had previously removed the CCTV
OL,11,Fdevices as part of a different
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,F"We thought we were paying for
OL,15,Fsecurity," she said.
OL,17,F"We thought we were paying for
OL,18,Finsurance, and it's not what it was. I
OL,19,Ffeel if they had them in place, then
OL,20,Fwe wouldn't have lost what we've lost".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FWhen asked if she would have left her
OL,7,Fbelongings there if she had known, she
OL,8,Fresponded: "No, definitely not.
OL,9,FWithout a doubt, I wouldn't have. You
OL,10,Fknow, I don't care about the presents
OL,11,For whatnot, but it's the memories I
OL,12,Fcan't get back".
OL,14,FKayleigh has received #2,000 from Pink
OL,15,FStorage but said she is frustrated by
OL,16,Fhow the company is dealing with all
OL,17,Fthose affected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FShe added: "What can we really do?
OL,7,FNothing other than just keep on to the
OL,8,Fcompany - that's what we've been doing
OL,9,Fand we've been blanked".
OL,11,FBethan and Richard said along with
OL,12,Fothers, they thought Pink Storage was
OL,13,Fgoing to ease the stress of what to do
OL,14,Fwith their belongings.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FBethan said: "Everybody that we've
OL,7,Fspoken to down there had their things
OL,8,Fthere because they were renovating a
OL,9,Fproperty or someone had passed away or
OL,10,Fthey were in ill health and they were
OL,11,Faccommodating family members and
OL,12,Fthings," Bethan said.
OL,14,F"Everybody was using Pink Storage as a
OL,15,Fsolution to a problem. They've just
OL,16,Fended up being a bigger problem".
OL,18,FScott Evans, Managing Director at Pink
OL,19,FStorage, said the company understands
OL,20,Fhow distressing this has been for the
OL,21,Fcustomers affected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FIn a statement, he said: "We are also
OL,7,Faware of five other self-storage
OL,8,Foperators in South Wales who have
OL,9,Fexperienced similar incidents that are
OL,10,Flikely linked. Our priority has been,
OL,11,Fand remains, supporting those impacted.
OL,13,F"All affected customers had contents
OL,14,Fprotection in place. Two claims have
OL,15,Falready been settled, with payments
OL,16,Fissued within 48 hours, and the
OL,17,Fremaining claims are currently being
OL,18,Freviewed and progressed.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,F"We have also implemented additional
OL,7,Fsecurity measures, including increased
OL,8,Fmonitoring, repairs, and physical
OL,9,Fpatrols, and we are continuing to
OL,10,Freview and strengthen site security."
OL,12,FSince the break-ins, it has been
OL,13,Frevealed that Pink Storage misled
OL,14,Fcustomers by stating the company was a
OL,15,F"proud member of the Self Storage
OL,16,FAssociation."
OL,18,FIts website stated: "This means we're
OL,19,Fcompliant with their high standards
OL,20,Fand rules while also being vetted by
OL,21,Ftheir team on an annual basis."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]wD@AOUxD@MO]zD@UOU}D@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FBut Self Storage Association Limited
OL,7,F(SSA UK) have since clarified that
OL,8,FPink Storage did not have SSA UK
OL,9,Fmembership.
OL,11,FSSA UK said in a statement: "We have
OL,12,Foffered significant support to Pink
OL,13,FSelf Storage Limited to map out the
OL,14,Fexact areas for improvement, and have
OL,15,Fprovided detailed notes on what needs
OL,16,Fto be done before they could be
OL,17,Fconsidered for membership of SSA UK.
OL,26,@sD@]OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,F"Despite several requests, Pink Self
OL,7,FStorage failed to remove an incorrect
OL,8,Fstatement on their website stating
OL,9,Fthat they are members of SSA UK,
OL,10,Fcompliant with our standards and
OL,11,Fvetted on an annual basis. All three
OL,12,Fof these statements are incorrect.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,F"We consider this statement to be
OL,7,F"passing off", i.e. by virtue of our
OL,8,Fsubstantial goodwill and reputation,
OL,9,Fthese actions amount to a
OL,10,Fmisrepresentation which is likely to
OL,11,Flead the public to believe that the
OL,12,Fservices that Pink Self Storage
OL,13,FLimited are providing are in some way
OL,14,Flinked to our organisation. This is
OL,15,Fnot the case, as we have pointed out
OL,16,Fto them on several occasions.
OL,18,F"We have written to request that they
OL,19,Fimmediately remove any reference to
OL,20,Fmembership of the Self Storage
OL,21,FAssociation UK from their website."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]zD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FPink Self Storage Limited now been
OL,7,Fexcluded from the SSA UK's Subscriber
OL,8,FScheme for breach of the relevant
OL,9,FTerms and Conditions.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police has confirmed it is
OL,12,Finvestigating reports of a break-in at
OL,13,Fseveral storage units at Pink Self
OL,14,FStorage on Langdon Road in Swansea,
OL,15,Fwhich is thought to have taken place
OL,16,Fon or some time prior to the weekend
OL,17,Fof January 31 - February 1.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774098664
OL,3,CCustomers distraught after losing
OL,4,Cthousands in storage unit break-in
OL,6,FThe force said: "The investigation has
OL,7,Fconfirmed that at least 19 storage
OL,8,Funits have been affected. The total
OL,9,Fvalue of the items stolen remains
OL,10,Fdetermined.
OL,12,F"The investigation into this incident
OL,13,Fremains ongoing. Any reports of damage
OL,14,For loss should be made to South Wales
OL,15,FPolice via 101, quoting occurrence
OL,16,F2600034696."
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/19
